I’ve seen a joint and I’ve smoked some too, and yeah it makes you tired, but give me a little and some cigarettes and cola/coffee to even it out and I can stay up and be high at the same time, it’s actually pretty nice, should try it sometime.

The only drug that has actually forced me into sleeping in a sense is DPH… Fun as hell though, you see all KINDS of shit, but eventually you just pass the hell out and wake up 12 hours later saying “wtf…?”.
